---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BrandIcon from '../components/ui/BrandIcon.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services - Inform Growth | AI-Native Revenue Infrastructure"
  description="We deploy a unified AI layer into your revenue stack. Shared context, compounding learnings, data that improves itself. From diagnosis to deployment in weeks, not months."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header geo-grid">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-content fade-up">
        <div class="header-eyebrow">AI-Native Revenue Infrastructure</div>
        <h1>We Bring the AI Layer.<br/>You Keep the Learnings.</h1>
        <p class="header-subtitle">
          Your RevOps stack was built for static workflows. AI requires real-time pipelines and cross-team learning systems. That's what we build.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Flow Section -->
  <section class="process-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="process-header fade-up">
        <h2>How We Work</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="process-steps fade-up">
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-num">01</span>
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3>Diagnose</h3>
          <p>Map your entire revenue stack. Run a data diagnostic across your CRM. Identify tool fragmentation, orphaned data, and where context is leaking between teams.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-connector"></div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-num">02</span>
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6"/><path d="M16 13H8"/><path d="M16 17H8"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3>Govern</h3>
          <p>Build your data dictionary. Define what each field means, who owns it, and how it flows between systems. Create validation rules that prevent garbage data at the source.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-connector"></div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-num">03</span>
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M12 2v4"/><path d="m6.34 6.34 2.83 2.83"/><path d="M2 12h4"/><path d="m6.34 17.66 2.83-2.83"/><path d="M12 18v4"/><path d="m17.66 17.66-2.83-2.83"/><path d="M18 12h4"/><path d="m17.66 6.34-2.83 2.83"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3>Deploy</h3>
          <p>Install the AI layer across your stack. Connect HubSpot, Salesforce, Outreach, and your other tools into a unified system. Enable shared context between Sales, Marketing, and CS.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-connector"></div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-num">04</span>
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3>Enable</h3>
          <p>Train your team on the new workflows. Build custom playbooks based on your top performers. Document everything so new hires ramp in weeks, not months.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-connector"></div>

        <div class="process-step highlighted">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-num">05</span>
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M12 2v4"/><path d="M12 18v4"/><path d="m4.93 4.93 2.83 2.83"/><path d="m16.24 16.24 2.83 2.83"/><path d="M2 12h4"/><path d="M18 12h4"/><path d="m4.93 19.07 2.83-2.83"/><path d="m16.24 7.76 2.83-2.83"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3>Compound</h3>
          <p>The system learns from every deal. Best practices get captured automatically. Tribal knowledge becomes institutional knowledge. Context never resets.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Build: The AI Infrastructure -->
  <section class="infrastructure-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="infra-header fade-up">
        <h2>The AI Layer We Deploy</h2>
        <p>Sales uses ChatGPT. Marketing has different tools. No one owns the outputs. We fix this with governed AI infrastructure.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="infra-grid fade-up">
        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <BrandIcon name="data-stack" size={32} />
          </div>
          <h3>Shared Context Across Teams</h3>
          <p>Sales, Marketing, and CS share one AI brain. When an operator closes a deal, everyone learns. When marketing finds messaging that converts, the system remembers. Context compounds instead of resetting.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <BrandIcon name="compounding" size={32} />
          </div>
          <h3>Learnings That Compound</h3>
          <p>Your best operator's objection handling. Your highest-converting email sequences. Your winning pricing strategies. Captured, systematized, and available to every team member - including future hires.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <BrandIcon name="integration" size={32} />
          </div>
          <h3>Data That Improves Itself</h3>
          <p>The AI layer continuously validates, enriches, and cleanses your data. What takes 20 hours of manual cleanup today becomes automatic. Your data debt decreases instead of compounds.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <BrandIcon name="security" size={32} />
          </div>
          <h3>Secure by Default</h3>
          <p>Read-only access unless you approve writes. Your credentials stay on your infrastructure. Every integration goes through human + automated QA before production.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <BrandIcon name="attribution" size={32} />
          </div>
          <h3>You Own Everything</h3>
          <p>We deploy on your infrastructure and hand you the keys. Every workflow, every integration, every definition - documented and ready for your team to maintain and extend.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="infra-card">
          <div class="infra-icon">
            <BrandIcon name="deep-scan" size={32} />
          </div>
          <h3>RevOps Gets Back to Strategy</h3>
          <p>Your RevOps team stops maintaining Salesforce and starts driving strategic initiatives. We handle the data plumbing. They focus on what actually moves revenue.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="infra-cta fade-up">
        <a href="/security" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More About Our Security Model</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Tiers -->
  <section class="tiers-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="tiers-header fade-up">
        <h2>Three Ways to Start</h2>
        <p>We bring our own AI tooling, so output ships fast. No 6-month discovery phases. No vendor evaluations. From diagnosis to deployment in weeks.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tiers-grid fade-up">
        <!-- Tier 1 -->
        <div class="tier-card">
          <div class="tier-label">Start Here</div>
          <h3>Deep-Scan</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Map every tool in your revenue stack. Find the leaks, fragmentation, and data debt. Quantify what it's costing you.</p>
          <div class="tier-guarantee">$100K+ in recoverable pipeline - or you don't pay.</div>
          <ul class="tier-includes">
            <li>CRM and data architecture audit</li>
            <li>Full revenue stack inventory</li>
            <li>Pipeline leak analysis</li>
            <li>Prioritized repair roadmap</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tier-meta">
            <span class="tier-price">$1,500</span>
            <span class="tier-time">1-2 weeks</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Book Deep-Scan</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Tier 2 -->
        <div class="tier-card featured">
          <div class="tier-label">Full Build</div>
          <h3>AI Layer Deployment</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Unified AI infrastructure across your entire revenue stack. Shared context. Compounding learnings. Data that improves itself.</p>
          <ul class="tier-includes">
            <li>Data cleanup and governance</li>
            <li>AI layer deployment</li>
            <li>Cross-team integrations</li>
            <li>Training and documentation</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tier-meta">
            <span class="tier-price">$15K-$40K</span>
            <span class="tier-time">6-12 weeks</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Scope Your Build</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Tier 3 -->
        <div class="tier-card">
          <div class="tier-label">Ongoing</div>
          <h3>Revenue Assurance</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">We operate inside your stack. Continuous monitoring, optimization, and support so your AI layer keeps compounding value.</p>
          <ul class="tier-includes">
            <li>24/7 monitoring and alerts</li>
            <li>Monthly data quality reports</li>
            <li>Quarterly strategic reviews</li>
            <li>New integration deployment</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tier-meta">
            <span class="tier-price">$3K-$5K/mo</span>
            <span class="tier-time">Ongoing</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Get Assurance</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="section bottom-cta geo-grid">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <h2>Ready to explore?</h2>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Book a Meeting</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Page Header */
  .page-header {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-base);
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .header-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Process Section */
  .process-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-surface);
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .header-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .header-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  /* Process Steps */
  .process-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .process-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--heading-color);
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .process-step {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .process-step:hover {
    border-color: var(--sky-blue);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .process-step.highlighted {
    background: var(--color-accent-muted);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .step-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-accent-muted);
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .process-step.highlighted .step-num {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-accent-muted);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .process-step.highlighted .step-icon {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .process-step h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .process-step p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .step-connector {
    width: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-connector::before {
    content: '→';
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .process-steps {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }

    .process-step {
      flex: 0 0 calc(50% - var(--space-md));
    }

    .step-connector {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .process-step {
      flex: 0 0 100%;
    }
  }

  /* Infrastructure Section */
  .infrastructure-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-base);
  }

  .infra-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .infra-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .infra-header p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .infra-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .infra-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .infra-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .infra-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .infra-card:hover {
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border-color: var(--sky-blue);
  }

  .infra-icon {
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .infra-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .infra-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .infra-cta {
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Tiers Section */
  .tiers-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-surface);
  }

  .tiers-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .tiers-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .tiers-header p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .tiers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .tiers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  .tier-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-subtle);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .tier-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--sky-blue);
  }

  .tier-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--sky-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(45, 80, 22, 0.15);
    position: relative;
  }

  .tier-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .tier-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .tier-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .tier-guarantee {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-accent-muted);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .tier-includes {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .tier-includes li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    position: relative;
  }

  .tier-includes li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .tier-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space-md) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .tier-price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
  }

  .tier-time {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
  }

  .btn-block {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Outcomes Section */
  .outcomes-section {
    background-color: var(--page-bg);
  }

  .outcomes-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .outcomes-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--heading-color);
  }

  .outcomes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .outcomes-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .outcome-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .outcome-stat {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .outcome-item p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Final CTA */
  .final-cta {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-base);
  }

  .final-cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .final-cta-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .final-cta h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .final-cta p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: #8C8880;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .btn-large {
    padding: 16px 32px;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  /* Scroll animations */
  .fade-up {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .fade-up.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* Bottom CTA */
  .bottom-cta {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-base);
  }

  .cta-box {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-box h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Scroll-triggered fade-up animations
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const fadeElements = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up');

    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        }
      });
    }, {
      threshold: 0.1,
      rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px'
    });

    fadeElements.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  });
</script>
